### 9 Demonstrations

#### 🧠 Self Control (Prism controlling itself)

| # | Title | What It Does |
|---|-------|-------------|
| S1 | **Agent Swarm Deployment** | Spawns 3 agents → creates a star-topology swarm → dispatches a research task → shows live telemetry → cleans up |
| S2 | **Guardian Health Check** | Triggers Guardian scheduled tasks → shows real-time health data → demonstrates AAB ledger → shows self-healing |
| S3 | **Governance Policy Audit** | Runs Tier 1 read-only → Tier 2 mutation with rollback → Tier 3 approval flow → shows policy divergence |

#### 🌐 Browser Control (Prism driving a browser)

| # | Title | What It Does |
|---|-------|-------------|
| B1 | **Web Research** | Opens browser session → navigates to docs page → extracts accessibility tree → captures screenshot → summarizes |
| B2 | **Multi-Page Navigation** | Navigates across 3 pages → captures screenshots at each → extracts key data → compiles report |
| B3 | **Form Interaction** | Navigates to form → fills text fields → selects dropdown → submits → verifies submission |

#### 💻 Computer Control (Prism executing system commands)

| # | Title | What It Does |
|---|-------|-------------|
| C1 | **System Diagnostics** | Runs `node --version`, `hostname`, `whoami` → captures output → writes diagnostic report to workspace |
| C2 | **Workspace File Operations** | Creates directory → writes file → reads back → appends content → lists directory → cleans up |
| C3 | **Process & Batch Execution** | Lists running processes → runs `start_web.bat` → monitors output → reports results |

#### 🎯 Tab Tour (after demos complete)

Cycles through every tab (Chat → Browser → Computer → Agents → Tools → Workspace → Settings → Telemetry → Logs → Scheduler → Watch Me → Network → Health) with a 3-second pause and a narration highlight for each.

