## Open Questions

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Browser demos**: The browser demos will use the existing browser sessions in the Browser tab. Should the demos use the Prism-internal browser (Playwright), or should they navigate within the dashboard's iframe? Currently designed to use the Playwright-managed sessions.

> [!NOTE]
> **start_web.bat**: Demo C3 references the canonical batch file at `D:\Projects\Prism\start_web.bat`. Is this the file you want used for the batch execution demonstration, or would you prefer a safer demo-specific script?

> [!NOTE]
> **Tab tour speed**: Currently designed with a 3-second pause per tab. Would you prefer faster (2s) or slower (5s) for the tour?

